#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.expanding.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.expanding"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:1 of
msgid "Return an expanding grouper, providing expanding functionality per group."
msgstr "返回一个扩展分组器，为每个分组提供扩展功能。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.expanding.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:4 of
msgid ""
"Minimum number of observations in window required to have a value; "
"otherwise, result is ``np.nan``."
msgstr "窗口中需要有值的最小观测数；否则结果为 ``np.nan``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:7 of
msgid ""
"If specified, the window will be shifted by `shift` rows (or data will be"
" shifted by `-shift` rows) before computing window function."
msgstr ""
"如果指定，窗口将在计算窗口函数之前按 `shift` 行进行偏移（或数据按 `-shift"
"` 行进行偏移）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:10 of
msgid ""
"If True, the window for current row is expanded from the last row to the "
"current instead of the first row."
msgstr "如果为 True，则当前行的窗口是从最后一行扩展到当前行，而不是从第一行开始。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.expanding.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.groupby`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:19 of
msgid "Apply a function groupby to a Series."
msgstr "对一个 Series 应用 groupby 函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.groupby`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.expanding.expanding:22 of
msgid "Apply a function groupby to each row or column of a DataFrame."
msgstr "对 DataFrame 的每一行或每一列应用 groupby 函数。"

